matching(String) - Method in class com.api.tenejob.controller.TeneJobController
The algorithm logic is as follows: Having a list of shifts, you go through and search within the list of availability of workers, when they "match", you count the number of coincidences, this is key, because we will only take those coincidences that your counter is one, and the following add this a matching list, and remove the worker from the list of workers, as this has been paired.
